parameters:
Passerby: "Aaaaah, a naked hunk is strutting around in front
of the station!! And he's... huge...!"

Passerby: "Is this like a shooting for a women's adult video
or something...? Even as a guy, I'm impressed by that
body..."

Anomalocaris: "Damn it... don't look... stop looking at
me...! Me... Anomalocaris, to suffer such humiliation...!!"

Anomalocaris, born as the second son of a karate dojo, won
trophies in numerous competitions but failed in job hunting
and became a monster... Now, stripped of all his pride and
dignity, he trembles in his birth-given form...

Anomalocaris: "Huff huff... If I defecate here, I can earn
the right to a rematch...! Then I can defeat that little
girl and return to the top of the organization...!! I'll do
it...!! Uoooooh...!!!"

Bunny-chan: "He's, he's passed out... The challenge is a
failure... There will be no rematch!! Please withdraw...
men! Someone take him away-!"

Memimi: "Anomalocaris... you didn't get your rematch, but I
fully acknowledge your resolve... I, I won't let anyone
laugh at you... yeah..."

Anomalocaris couldn't escape his position as a low-ranking
member of the organization, but he gained a sudden surge of
female fans in the city and even came to be respected by his
fellow organization members...
